high_descs: Turn right, go to the fridge on the left.
Take the orange cup out of the fridge.
Turn around, bring the cup to the sink.
Put the cup in the sink.
Pick up the knife nearest you on the counter, left of the sink.
Put the knife in the cup in the sink.
anns.task_desc: Put a knife in a cup in the sink.

high_descs: Turn right and move past the counter on the right and then turn left and face the refrigerator once past the green recycling bin.
Open the refrigerator, pick up the amber cup to the left of the pan from the center shelf, then close the refrigerator door.
Turn around and move to the sink between the range and the dishwasher.
Place the amber cup to the rear of the drain in the sink.
From the area to the left of the sink, pick up the knife between the spoon and the fork.
Place the knife in the cup in the sink.
anns.task_desc: Place a cup containing a knife in the sink.

high_descs: Walk towards the round wooden table, then hang a right and walk over to the fridge.
Open the fridge and take the wooden cup out of the fridge, then close the door.
Turn right and take a step forward, turn right again and walk over to the sink.
Put the wooden cup in the back of the sink.
Pick up the rightmost butter knife off of the counter to the left of the sink.
Put the butter knife in the wooden cup that is in the sink.
anns.task_desc: Put a butter knife in a wooden cup in the sink.
